{"tid":1814180,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"乃木坂46討論區#289：白石麻衣卒業おめでとう","createTime":"2020-01-06T21:03:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-11T07:36:26.000Z","uid":19533,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"70de7cad6d10e2db85f828195a60b37a8cc957f4","tid":1814180,"uid":19533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T21:03:03.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>乃Po呼籲: <br />\n「25單全握迷白苦行」<br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wdCXAVc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwdCXAVc.jpg&h=bf82b7ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WyivVNg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWyivVNg.jpg&h=f101eaf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8kZV63v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8kZV63v.jpg&h=7a22b8d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">乃木坂46(Nogizaka46)</span> 是一個日本大型女子偶像團體，為另一著名女子團體AKB48的「官方對手／正式對手」（公式ライバル），因此其行銷策略與AKB48的姐妹團體&mdash;&mdash;SKE48、NMB48、HKT48等不同，但總製作人同樣是秋元康，且與其他姊妹團體之間仍常有跨團體的合作或競賽企畫。團體名字中的「46」讀作「Forty-six／フォーティシックス」，而不是讀作「四十六／よんじゅうろく」。包含一至四期生在內，團體目前共有43名成員，而隊長為秋元真夏。其與2015年8月21日成立的櫸坂46、以及2019年2月11日自櫸坂46獨立的日向坂46，構成大型偶像組合系列「坂道系列」。<br />\n乃木坂46是作為AKB48的「官方對手」而成立的女子團體，因此跟AKB48的「姊妹團體」（如SKE48等）不同。例如團體不像AKB48及其姊妹團體般擁有AKB48劇場、NMB48劇場等專屬表演場地。團名取自坐落東京都赤坂地區乃木坂的「SME乃木坂大樓」，該建築為所屬唱片公司日本索尼音樂的前辦公大樓之一。根據秋元康所說，<span style=\"color: red;\">「46」象徵：「就算人數比AKB48少，也具有不遜於AKB48的幹勁</span>」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">成員名單:</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nogizaka46.com/member/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nogizaka46.com%2Fmember%2F&d=uPV0Czv%2B0bylLCB0p4n6nAZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=5b55fa9a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nogizaka46.com/member/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">-NEWS-</div><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">乃木坂46 24thシングル<br />\n「夜明けまで強がらなくてもいい」<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">發售中</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EeYNpoM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEeYNpoM.png&h=1c0202b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n桜井玲香2nd写真集『視線』<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">發售中</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p0h8R54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp0h8R54.jpg&h=dc9fd472&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n衛藤美彩フォトブック『Decision』<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2020年1月8日発売</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B1uOBES.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB1uOBES.jpg&h=033ccd13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n山下美月1st写真集『忘れられない人』<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2020年1月21日発売</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dTTDep3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdTTDep3.jpg&h=9c3fba6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n堀未央奈2nd写真集『タイトル未定』<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2020年発売</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4pLrGQD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4pLrGQD.jpg&h=7a8f974b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">乃木坂46成員列表 (最新)</span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/55jjZ5r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F55jjZ5r.png&h=49fb8707&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GNvbRca.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGNvbRca.png&h=4cbd3c30&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RAQ7pxc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRAQ7pxc.png&h=cb84f029&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0CDQniT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0CDQniT.png&h=e765757c&s={SIZE}\" /></div></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">[size=5]<span style=\"color: red;\">歡迎新人加入</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://nogizaka46-dc.com/sort/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnogizaka46-dc.com%2Fsort%2F&d=uPV0Czv%2B0bylLCB0p4n6nAZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=9d42d896\" target=\"_blank\">http://nogizaka46-dc.com/sort/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://andykwanfai.github.io/nogizaka46-sort/#/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fandykwanfai.github.io%2Fnogizaka46-sort%2F%23%2F&d=uPV0Czv%2B0bylLCB0p4n6nAZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=ac877d8c\" target=\"_blank\">https://andykwanfai.github.io/nogizaka46-sort/#/</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://keyakizaka46style.com/sort/nogizaka46sort.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fkeyakizaka46style.com%2Fsort%2Fnogizaka46sort.html&d=uPV0Czv%2B0bylLCB0p4n6nAZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=cd700efd\" target=\"_blank\">http://keyakizaka46style.com/sort/nogizaka46sort.html</a></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請新/舊手足定期體檢</span></span></div><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Q&amp;A</div></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">1）那乃木坂乃何許人也？<br />\n簡單來說，乃木坂是來自日本的偶像組合，演戲唱歌跳舞等全部都會參與，是正統全能型偶像。<br />\n<br />\n2）那裡可以購買乃木坂既有關產品（生寫、CD、海報、寫真集、演唱會等）？<br />\n一般來說，信和地庫會有存貨，不過價錢就...另外有不少商品需於官方WEBSHOP購入，不過這裡有機會提供代購,，要看看手足們的心情。<br />\n<br />\n3）這裡可否討論其他非46的成員？<br />\n我們一般不會阻止，但請適量討論。皆因這裡主要討論46GRP,你也可作理性討論，攻擊、黑其他成員,但請先作好世界大戰的準備。<br />\n<br />\n4）那麼我要如何見到乃木坂成員？<br />\n直接飛去日本或中國參加握手會、演唱會、見面會，但不要幻想會再來港，因香港已經柒出國際。詳細辦法請向手足查詢。<br />\n<br />\n5）除了46GRP,有什麼值得推薦？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"6a1e9a39687de37fd40d195d69b19f5124a6db46","tid":1814180,"uid":61389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T21:05:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YTmhAX1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYTmhAX1.jpg&h=b8af1b6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nLM<br />\n陣間落街睇下報紙先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0cf60218c8c9d66b6e6c148606472f25a655b64","tid":1814180,"uid":19533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T21:06:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hy3zDbC.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhy3zDbC.gif&h=8365f796&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UeFBRwD.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUeFBRwD.gif&h=59967f6d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3W6A640.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3W6A640.gif&h=e00d00c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n白麻三連call<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ef0cba324e2f67bc94bb73514817f4d246051e5","tid":1814180,"uid":285411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T21:07:22.000Z","msg":"LMai<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GAhkyLo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGAhkyLo.jpg&h=774b461b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1f5dd1a7960658616b9fc1abfb39e651535ea5ad","tid":1814180,"uid":324792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T21:07:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CyMA64S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCyMA64S.jpg&h=2194f72b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<st